        <p class="pt-3 w-75 m-auto">
            I'm in the final year of Bachelor of Information Technology at the Southern Institute of Technology in Invercargill campus. I am a programmer who loves programming and keeps <strong class="text-white">research</strong> and <strong class="text-white">learning</strong> new skills related in IT, and I would like to be a full-stack in future.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center border-div-trigger w-200px m-auto pt-2">
            <a class="text-decoration-none" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact">Contact with me now</a>
